N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4812.6 - Distribution of copies by clerk

State Regulations

The clerk of the municipality shall prepare the license
in triplicate, issuing the original to the licensee, retaining a copy and
forwarding a copy to the local law enforcement agency. Notes
